full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/28/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE Immigration and Naturalization Service 300 North Los Angeles Street Los Angeles, California 90012 AUTHORIZED CIVIL SURGEONS IMPORTANT: As soon as you receive this notice you are required to make arrangements immediately for your medical examination. You are instructed to arrange for an appointment with one of the following medical examiners who will perform the required laboratory and x-ray pro- cedures as well as the medical examination. The total cost of this examination will be more than $32.50 which amount is required to be paid by you. The results of the medical examination must be presented at your immigra- tion interview as scheduled. X-RAY REPORT IS NOT NECESSARY FOR CHILD 10 YEARS OF AGE OR UNDER. SEROLOGY TEST IS NOT NECESSARY FOR CHILD 14 YEARS OF AGE OR UNDER. LOS ANGELES COUNTY RIVERSIDE COUNTY Michael S. Burton, M. D. John T. Lanier, M. D.
